{"tid":338993,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"最近跑步都腳痛","createTime":"2017-07-28T16:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T16:37:17.000Z","uid":58699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6824004e2006359ae69fea8fa3e11b877d8e53a7","tid":338993,"uid":58699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T16:09:45.000Z","msg":"跑左有1個半月<br />\n通常隔一兩日跑一次 每次都有拉足筋（我自己認為拉夠）<br />\n大概都30分鐘跑5k左右<br />\n但係最近換左對m記跑鞋 第一次著 突然跑到32分鐘6.3k<br />\n跑完呢次之後過左一日再跑 一跑對膝頭同腳掌都痛<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650bdadf955c834c355f1f74dd999a7612c89dc1","tid":338993,"uid":58699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T16:20:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80d92da6f1c7af5e38a183edcb02542f96f227b8","tid":338993,"uid":21896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T16:23:57.000Z","msg":"腳掌唔知,但膝頭應該跑步姿勢有問題,試下跑個時提高D腿"},{"pid":"aaf0fe5308f74347a0f010ad5ff8673f27950109","tid":338993,"uid":2477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T16:37:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>腳掌唔知,但膝頭應該跑步姿勢有問題,試下跑個時提高D腿</blockquote><br />\n岩<br />\n如果你咁持續落去有機會壓力落晒係小腿徑骨<br />\nGoogle下姿勢跑法"}]}